        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🖼️ Product Mockup Generator\n\nFrom a product description, an agent invents lifestyle scenes, then renders mockups and applies a brightness/contrast polish.\n\n**Pipeline:** Inputs → Scene agent → Prompt list → Image gen → Color polish\n\n**Try this:** raise the scene count or change the target audience."
